Is it that example or some other code you are having trouble with, 
cos the example worked fine here.

> Ok, that's my code, and where it says FreeBitMap_ that's where things
> go weird, maybe I should use FreeMem_ and do it that way?  I don't

No, the way bitmaps are allocated may change in the future, and you 
can't secodn guess it by freeing it in a different way than it is 
supposed to be.


