Well, it should - or at least, it shouldn't work while in Blitz mode.

None of the OS functions should be used while in Blitz mode, since the OS is
disabled...

Maybe you are going into QAmiga mode or something?


I have found that sometimes, for whatever reason, things that shouldn't work
did on my system.  But it usually turned out later that it wouldn't work on
other people's systems, so be careful... 

