Hi,

Hurrah!  I'm also personally more interested in the PPC (Pheonix Platform Consortium) than Amiga themseleves, since I believe that the people involved are more in-line with the community's ideas than Amiga themselves are.

So, I'll be joing up as well, since PPC deserves to be a success, and at last, maybe the community (the ones who know what we're on about) can give the Amiga what it deserves.

Note: I'm not dropping the Amiga what so ever!  If I was dropping the Amiga, I'd be following Amiga themselves.... :-)

