I got it to work (in my C code), by obtaining the printer's copy of
preferences, and then changing them, this works fine.  I have posted a new
email with more info (thought without code it's probably difficult to
understand :-( ).  I'll send the C code tommorrow, and we'll see what
happens, I'll also tryu what you just suggested.  Thanks!

