Hello Mathias
>> Been adding commands to it.. Is anyone interested in the updates?
> 
> Err, what I'm interested in is to know exactly what I have to use to
> program a MUI application. EFMUILib is not the only way ?

No it`s not the only way, you could use the MUI Library directly
by converting the FD.
There are a few tag setting commands in Intuition library that
MUI uses a lot as well. (IE, MUISet() calls SetAttrsA_)

It`s not actually that much different not using the EFMUILib,
Just a lot easier with EFMUILib, why WOULDN`T you want to use it?

