Hi Curt

> I need to determine the EvenByteWidth required for a given image pixel
> width.
> 
> I am using the method shown in the small example that is attached.
> 
> It seems to work OK - but is there a better way?

Try doing:

(width + 15) & $FFF0

That should round it up to the nearest 16.


