On Tue, 23 Nov 1999, John Mason wrote:

> Yep, you use IntuitionBase\Firstscreen.  But you have to lock
> IntuitionBase first, like this:
> lock.l = LockIBase_(0)
> FirstScreen.Screen = IntuitionBase\*FirstScreen
> UnlockIBase_ lock

Actually I had to do this for something else today, and it's more like
this:

  lock.l = LockIBase_(0) 
  *ibase.IntuitionBase = IntuitionBase --
  *firstscreen.Screen = (*ibase\FirstScreen)  
  UnlockIBase_(lock) 

