Date: Tue, 02 Nov 1999 20:00:28 +0000
Subject: GTShape Q's
X-UIDL: 681e2ff51bff2285eaa93460f9e55271

Hello,

I've just now been trying to use GTShape command and am having probs.
Can someone answer thes questions

Can a loaded GTShape display more than the 4 colours.
(I'm loading in a 256 colour shape but it is only getting displayed in the
first 4 cols) (YES, I've opened a 256 col screen)

Also can they have the flag of $80 (GadgetDown) specified.
(I've tried it but my loop which is checking never gets a message from the
gadget down, YES, Ive added IDCMP of GADGET_DOWN)

I've not used the GTShape command before, and wondering wether there's prob
with it. (There was in one version)

Any help would be welcome.

Cya,

    Leigh.

