I'm hoping James's stuff will help.  Hold And Modify, no Horrendous and Mmmmmjsjwjsji, I can't think of M, but, yes it was great in 1987, but in 1999, it's gviving me real agro... :) (No disrespect to Jay Miner and all other past Amiga gurus...)

But, in *theory*, Gfx. Card remapping should be easier.... (for some reason I have a terrible cough after saying that....) :)

