Subject: HomeLand - A new RTS game
Date: Tue, 16 Nov 1999 07:41:49 PST
X-UIDL: 39f4896fcac397e30dc1db30e23f3582

Hi all,

Have you seen the new demo on my homepage, called HomeLand it´s a new 
real-time strategy game, with some original features. You can create you own 
customizible units(with some limitations ofcourse). These units are created 
from tecnologies that you research. There are currently only 14 different 
technologies, but it´s due to expand. Any suggestions and ideas are welcome, 
so please email me if you think of something cool to be added. Screenshots 
and download are available from my homepage.

Jeppe Nielsen

