Well, here are some ideas - but just ideas, these would have to be tested by
someone who actually HAS a middle-mouse button...

Maybe the GameB(port) command would return a recognizable value for it?  It
returns 127 on my system for the right mouse button  (but nothing for the
left)

Maybe JoyB(port) really does return a different value for it?

Maybe Mbuttons returns a value for it?
Left  button down=1
Right button down=2
Left  button up  =5
Right button up  =6

Makes you wonder what happened to 3 & 4, doesn't it??? 

