Hi,

Slightly off-topic (non blitz related!), but deja.com have ran a poll on
operating systems to see which one was best, you will never guess but our
beloved AmigaDOS came FIRST, TOP, NUMERO UNO bla bla :)  

Visit http://x24.deja.com/rate/list_items.xp?CID=12029&PCID=11878&N=0 to see
for yourself (sorry for the rather weird URL!)

Second was OS/2 (IBMs and MSs old 32bit OS attempt), followed by BeOS and in
fourth (Amiga should take note of this, but they won't!) is Linux!!!!!

It should be noted that Windoze '98, '95, 3.x, NT, 2000 Beta and MS-DOS were
pretty much at the BOTTOM!  Funnily enough, MS-DOS beat Windows '98, '95 and
3.x!!!  Ha Ha! :)  

Oh, well, just nice to let you know.... :) 

