Hi Martin

> The command pointer doesn't seem to work with the display library. And
> I want to have the mouse cursor moved the whole time so displaysprite
> does not work.

If you set up an interrupt you can do it:

SetInt 5
    DisplaySprite 0,x,y
End SetInt


