>    i'm back after a long time away and I have two questions.

Welcome back, definately was a long time. Still working on TC?

>    Does anyone know how to use the polygon command? One of the
>    parameters
> asks for a list of coords but no-where in the manual does it suggest
> how this list of coords is to be supplied.

I think its just an array of x/y co-ordionates:

NEWTYPE.coord
  x.w
  y.w
END NEWTYPE

Dim blah.coord(10)
blah(0)\x=0,0
; and so on

Poly ....,num_of_points,&blah(0)


