On 23-Nov-99, Christopher Jarvis wrote.

> Hello.
>   i'm back after a long time away and I have two questions.
>   Did mildred end up supporting polygon commands?
>   Does anyone know how to use the polygon command? One of the parameters
> asks for a list of coords but no-where in the manual does it suggest how
> this list of coords is to be supplied.

Mildred doesn't support polygons, but if you don't need filled then you can
use Mline to do polygons.

Planar poly and polyf take just pointer to array of coords as David
explaned.

