> for For-Next loops etc, as well- I don't know how important they are
> though. 

    StooooooP. PowerD is based on AmigaE which already got these features
and of course, it's easy to do that. PureBasic is started from scratch and
all must be added, time after time. About multiple return code, just share
some variables, and you get it.

    Ho, is PowerD support the PPC 100% ? look very interesting :)

        Good bye,

