> s=val(left$(a$,1)) 
> 
> the problem here is letters and non-numeric characters produce a 0.. I
> need the 0 though coz my program uses it (No way around)..

You could do this;

x=Asc(a$)

If x>=48 And x<=57
  do numeric stuff with val(a$)
Else
  do letter stuff
End If

Remembering that 48-57 are the ASCII values of 0-9.


Regards,

        Sandy Brownlee

