Hi Bippy

> What TAGS do I supply to get gadgets to have their titles somewhere
> else other than on the left ? eg..
> 
>      +-------+ This is how it is openening      +-------+
> LIFE | Press | I need it to open like the       | Press | LIFE
>      +-------+ one on the right!                +-------+

It should be the gadget flags - just or in one of these values:

#PLACETEXT_LEFT
#PLACETEXT_RIGHT
#PLACETEXT_ABOVE
#PLACETEXT_BELOW
#PLACETEXT_IN


