Hi Bippy

> NResetTagList #GTCB_Scaled , 1
>  NAddTag #GTCB_Checked, 0
>  NAddTag #PLACETEXT_RIGHT, 1
> NCheckBoxGadget 10, 15, gh*5+20, gh*2, gh, "CDRWIN", taglistt
> 
> and it still doesnt work :(

They're not tags, they're part of the flags parameter (if there is 
one, I don't use NCS much).

Yep, its NSetGadgetFlags #PLACETEXT_RIGHT

You'll probably need to set it back to left afterwards or all the 
texts will appear on the right.


